Network Features

KanTrack operates in local-first mode by default and does not require network connectivity.
Optional cloud features (such as account-based backup or synchronization) may use network connectivity only when explicitly enabled by the user.

Official Distribution

Only versions distributed by BTi — BosslessTechIndustries are considered official KanTrack releases.
All other uses are unauthorized.

